Actions.Text: COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO HEALTH

Title: Extends the provisions of law authorizing certain health care professionals licensed to practice in other jurisdictions to practice in this state in connection with an event sanctioned by New York Road Runners
Summary: Extends provisions of law authorizing certain health care professionals licensed to practice in other jurisdictions to practice in this state in connection with an event sanctioned by New York Road Runners or the World Triathlon Corporation.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend chapter 192 of the laws of 2011, relating to authorizing certain health care professionals licensed to practice in other jurisdictions to practice in this state in connection with an event sanctioned by New York Road Runners, in relation to including the World Triathlon Corporation and extending the provisions thereof
